  <brief_title>The Relationship Between Erythrocyte Transfusion and Nutrition and Necrotizing Enterocolitis in Preterm Infants</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigation of the Relationship Between Erythrocyte Transfusion and Nutrition and Necrotizing Enterocolitis in Preterm Infants: a Randomized Controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
