  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study; The aim of this study was to investigate the changes in fasting and dietary
      and mesenteric blood flow in the acute period during and after transfusion and to evaluate
      the necrotizing enterocolitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
